org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl

Class GridContainerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl.GridContainerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Container, GridContainer, Primitive

    public class GridContainerImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements GridContainer
    An implementation of the model object 'Grid Container'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Name
    • Columns
    • Equal Width
    • Children
    • Horizontal Spacing
    • Vertical Spacing
    • Margin Width
    • Margin Height
